metadata.name: CryptoRejects NFT #1
metadata.description:
The uniquely hand-designed Crypto rejects are inspired by the idea of a second chance to win in crypto. 

We have stepped up and set a high standard for ourselves and the project. We want to invite all to chase the journey with Us and explore the life-changing opportunities these NFTs will value with new state-of-the-art utilities and design. 

Quit looking for that next big thing and take a step back and go back to traditional NFT roots. #1
